{"tid":198740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好傍偟，家庭問題","createTime":"2017-04-12T17:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T04:40:25.000Z","uid":81818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a63b8c604c2b5ad2ecf8bad3c90298210b4b7a6","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:07:52.000Z","msg":"啱啱老豆老母嗌大交，講話要離婚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且之前都有試過好多次，但今次講到實牙實齒。起因係老豆做生意(辛苦工)俾人爭數(類似，實則唔清楚，更複雜)，阿媽就不停講，不停嘈(內容類似:點解之前唔聽我講&hellip;&hellip;)。老豆起初都忍到，之後佢就爆。大聲鬧我阿媽，跟住對罵，我阿媽一發癲就亂黎，啱啱掉爛咗個滑鼠同瓷杯。之前試過拎菜刀叫老豆砍佢，又試過要咬舌自盡，嗰時嚇到我報警。我媽見我報警至冷靜番。<br />\n<br />\n宜家唔知要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好彩差唔多考曬DSE。<br />\n如果前幾日攪壇咁嘅嘢真係唔撚使考。<br />\n<br />\n大家俾啲意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry,可能講得唔清楚"},{"pid":"df1474addcfea43326f8cf978a79a856269a4576","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ceb944be5b2368e9a25186402faa3af5b5624a","tid":198740,"uid":93807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:10:08.000Z","msg":"家家有本難唸的經...加油..."},{"pid":"6f715267b0ca50ee60b7f78ec113a419c75f9f18","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家家有本難唸的經...加油...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5135fdcf9b987a7641738f79378c10c8d5e739","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:26:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757023fb3c1de1e738a931c0b585c5689ae43b70","tid":198740,"uid":84587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"婚姻係佢地既  佢地離你都冇計 <br />\n有咩事多d遷就佢地 <br />\n佢地吵架 諗下有冇方法 調和佢地"},{"pid":"9a1feeb946c17d105033e983ed6a12c638e58460","tid":198740,"uid":101393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:32:40.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗搵下婚姻輔導 有個第三者/旁觀者傾可能好d. 你會唔會勸下佢地試下用呢個方法解決問題<br />\n就算要行到離婚呢一步 都起碼叫做平心靜氣傾過下 好過暴力解決"},{"pid":"81f24417868e27a6d2696c2b1450bbc5c51ee094","tid":198740,"uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:36:19.000Z","msg":"錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢兩個問題黎，你可以點解決，你都18歲，仲會為左你而隔硬一齊咩⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n共富貴共患難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4a97fd67e96ef673d4f897ce10bb3fa6da0264","tid":198740,"uid":58722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"盡量抽身, 出多D街搵多D野做分散下注意力<br />\n<br />\n我同你情況差唔多<br />\n<br />\n唔知你父母會唔會聽你勸<br />\n<br />\n我父母就一定唔會<br />\n<br />\n所以久而久之都廢鳩事理佢地D野<br />\n<br />\n著緊既只令自己傷心心煩<br />\n<br />\n考完DSE 既可以做下PT<br />\n<br />\n一來搵下錢, 二來用工作麻醉下自己<br />\n<br />\n除非你好有信心啦, 如果唔係都真係唔好差隻腳埋去<br />\n<br />\n自從佢地開始愈吵愈大鑊, 我最開心最放鬆既時間就係返工出街去旅行果D唔係屋企既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能我對自己父母已無期望, 比較消極, 請勿見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b0e09a2e59bccdd902abc1b88f295b7fe5735b","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗唔洗搵下婚姻輔導 有個第三者/旁觀者傾可能好d. 你會唔會勸下佢地試下用呢個方法解決問題<br />\n就算要行到離婚呢一步 都起碼叫做平心靜氣傾過下 好過暴力解決</blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得阿媽有啲情緒病。<br />\n我應該點開口叫佢睇醫生？"},{"pid":"3afe52db53cf2fa8b85c78a04a377e0ec954f3b1","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盡量抽身, 出多D街搵多D野做分散下注意力<br />\n<br />\n我同你情況差唔多<br />\n<br />\n唔知你父母會唔會聽你勸<br />\n<br />\n我父母就一定唔會<br />\n<br />\n所以久而久之都廢鳩事理佢地D野<br />\n<br />\n著緊既只令自己傷心心煩<br />\n<br />\n考完DSE 既可以做下PT<br />\n<br />\n一來搵下錢, 二來用工作麻醉下自己<br />\n<br />\n除非你好有信心啦, 如果唔係都真係唔好差隻腳埋去<br />\n<br />\n自從佢地開始愈吵愈大鑊, 我最開心最放鬆既時間就係返工出街去旅行果D唔係屋企既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能我對自己父母已無期望, 比較消極, 請勿見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，本來佢地開始吵嗰時都唔想理。<br />\n但老母會擲嘢同老豆動手，冇得唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0b2a48ff7f07c0cdb1c83251a05be9f6c52874","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢兩個問題黎，你可以點解決，你都18歲，仲會為左你而隔硬一齊咩⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n共富貴共患難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有個F2細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb807c8decfda113a8c9156c0ec8b2b85fda8f1","tid":198740,"uid":92273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:46:01.000Z","msg":"你話要跳樓囉，大鳩佢地"},{"pid":"e50c8755968eae96f4f3a4ed4ed25b665154e068","tid":198740,"uid":70907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:49:14.000Z","msg":"最緊要唔好做傻事 做好自己 考埋個試先 加油"},{"pid":"f3534512702b7cf7b731801c871072b02fc0176e","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要唔好做傻事 做好自己 考埋個試先 加油</blockquote><br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"06fb378b844864f6fd1e71d99ade43ab475e61c4","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話要跳樓囉，大鳩佢地</blockquote><br />\n之前阿媽衝口而出講過一齊跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a52b6b1fd393a0e6f4e670303dec6645752a8b","tid":198740,"uid":92831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會帶到媽媽睇醫生？"},{"pid":"d4b59fbc45ab4ab9c541974b124d48b6eb36c1a1","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會帶到媽媽睇醫生？</blockquote><br />\n唔知點開口"},{"pid":"750c88206d0d6ec1afc3f3436106f57c9fcce950","tid":198740,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:55:41.000Z","msg":"徬徨"},{"pid":"6eab2023e46a96a07be342cf7a9e98e9afa2d2bc","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:56:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>徬徨</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb4ae35d25a9b486deff507229954319757bd56","tid":198740,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:57:23.000Z","msg":"望番個用戶名真係諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adca4e1ad80d10cacb0ff07973c66970319285e","tid":198740,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:57:45.000Z","msg":"我都係 父母如今已經離左婚 日子都係咁過 只係窮d"},{"pid":"b8f2549aadcbca0d1cbeab822ad3329633f42699","tid":198740,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗搵下婚姻輔導 有個第三者/旁觀者傾可能好d. 你會唔會勸下佢地試下用呢個方法解決問題<br />\n就算要行到離婚呢一步 都起碼叫做平心靜氣傾過下 好過暴力解決</blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得阿媽有啲情緒病。<br />\n我應該點開口叫佢睇醫生？</blockquote><br />\n睇醫生食藥其實都係暫時性<br />\n可以舒緩你呀媽嘅情緒<br />\n但同時間啲藥會令人冇咁敏銳<br />\n最緊要係解決導致壓力嘅源頭<br />\n即係老豆嘅金錢問題 同 呀媽對你老豆困境嘅理解+過份緊張？<br />\n<br />\n多啲同你呀媽單獨傾計<br />\n等佢有個渠道可以發洩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335a6ededfab47ec07e46912bce21e4ed649ef63","t